Description: In this latest volume, Naruto stands up to Tobi and the Allied Shinobi Forces battle the Ten-Tailed Beast.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 64
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: A teenager signs up to help mythical creatures assimilate into society. How will he handle being roommates with a sexy snake woman, an alluring centaur girl and a harpy who likes to flirt?
Title: MONSTER MUSUME, VOL. 2
Author: Okayado

Description: Yuma forms the Numbers Club, whose purpose is to discover new Numbers Cards and foil the evil plans of Dr. Faker.
Title: YU-GI-OH! ZEXAL, VOL. 4
Author: Shin Yoshida and Naohito Miyoshi
Contributor: by Shin Yoshida and Naohito Miyoshi

Description: The 104th Training Corps stop for a much-needed respite in Utgard Castle, but their plans to rest are foiled when they discover that the Titans are now attacking at night.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 10
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: The son of a notorious gangster gets caught in a love triangle with his childhood sweetheart and the daughter of his father's rival.
Title: NISEKOI: FALSE LOVE, VOL. 1
Author: Naoshi Komi

Description: Himura Kenshin is a former assassin who has sworn to never again draw his sword unless it is to help someone in need. But will he be able to keep this oath?
Title: RUROUNI KENSHIN: RESTORATION, VOL. 2
Author: Nobuhiro Watsuki

Description: Ageha learns a new power that will allow him to manipulate the laws of gravity and Elmore has a horrible vision of the future.
Title: PSYREN, VOL. 14
Author: Toshiaki Iwashiro

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Max and the Flock travel to Antarctica to help a group of environmental scientists studying the affects of global warming.
Title: MAXIMUM RIDE: THE MANGA, VOL. 7
Author: James Patterson and NaRae Lee
Contributor: by James Patterson and NaRae Lee

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 1
Author: Yana Toboso
